          SHORT="A language and environment for statistical computing"

cat << EOF
R is a language and environment for statistical computing and graphics. It
provides a wide variety of statistical (linear and nonlinear modelling,
classical statistical tests, time-series analysis, classification, clustering)
and graphical techniques, and is highly extensible. The S language is often the
vehicle of choice for research in statistical methodology, and R provides an
open source route to participation in that activity.
EOF
